      "content": "Your feelings of invisibility are valid, but it's a tragic misconception that stopping would mean no one notices or cares; people rely on your connections and kindness more than you realize. This thought of disappearing is a serious symptom of deep isolation and not a peaceful solution to loneliness, as there is real pain behind it. Please consider reaching out to a trusted human friend immediately or contacting the 988 Lifeline to hear that you matter, because you are here and someone needs to hear you today.",
